title: Switzerland Explains Air Incident With Russia as 'Lack of Coordination'
text: The head of the Foreign Affairs Committee of the lower house of Russia's parliament said that Switzerland said an aviation incident involving a Russian aircraft carrying members of parliament and a Swiss fighter jet near the border with France had occurred due to a failed coordination. ...
